text: Xenia Knoll and Amra Sadiković were the defending champions, but both players chose not to participate. Andreea Mitu and Elena-Gabriela Ruse won the title, defeating Laura Pigossi and Maryna Zanevska in the final, 4–6, 6–3, [10–4]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Montreux Ladies Open - Doubles
title: 2018 Montreux Ladies Open – Doubles
